An Employer Implores 

Let me ignore your aches and pains, 

Those things on which you dwell 

In hope one day I can report 

That you have called in well. 

-- Ralph Shaffer. 

Man-Made Terms? 

The neighborhood ladies chat every day, 

Or kaffeeklatsch if you prefer, 

A practice reserved for the female sex; 

The men at the office confer] 

-- Gerry Tamm. 

